$$mgy = \frac{1}{2} m v^2 \Rightarrow v = \sqrt{2gy}$$

即

$$v \cdot \frac {1} {\sqrt {y}} = \sqrt {2g} = \text{Const}$$

不失一般性, 考虑

$$v \cdot f(x, y) = \text{C}$$

曲线设为$x(t), y(t)$

则

$$ds = \sqrt {(dx)^2 + (dy)^2} = \sqrt {\dot x^2 + \dot y^2} dt$$

$$dt = \frac{ds}{v} = \text{C} f(x, y) ds = \text{C} f \sqrt {\dot x^2 + \dot y^2} dt$$

要求用时$T$最小

$$T = \int dt = C \int f \sqrt {\dot x^2 + \dot y^2} dt$$

根据哈密顿原理有:

$$\frac{\partial L}{\partial \boldsymbol {q}}-\frac{d}{dt}\frac{\partial L}{\partial \dot{\boldsymbol {q}}}=0$$

where 

$$L = f \sqrt {\dot x^2 + \dot y^2}$$

由于本题 

$$
\begin{align*}
f &amp;= f(y) \\
\Rightarrow \frac{\partial f}{\partial x} &amp;= 0 \\
\Rightarrow \frac{\partial L}{\partial x} &amp;= 0
\end{align*}
$$

故只需考虑$x$方向

$$\frac{d}{dt}\frac{\partial L}{\partial \dot{x}}=0$$

故

$$\frac{\partial L}{\partial \dot{x}}=C$$

即

$$\frac{\dot x}{\sqrt {\dot x^2 + \dot y^2}} f = C$$

$$
\begin{align*}
&amp;\quad \frac{\dot x}{\sqrt {\dot x^2 + \dot y^2}} f = C \\
&amp;\Rightarrow \frac{1}{\sqrt {1 + (y^{\prime})^2}} f = C \\
&amp;\Rightarrow \frac{1}{\sqrt {1 + (y^{\prime})^2}} \frac {1} {\sqrt {y}} = C \\
&amp;\Rightarrow y(1 + (y^{\prime})^2) = C \\
\end{align*}
$$

注意到

$$\sin^2 \alpha (1+ \cot^2 \alpha) = 1$$

令

$$
\begin{cases}
y &amp;= C \sin^2 \alpha \\
y^{\prime} &amp;= \cot \alpha
\end{cases}
$$

则

$$
\begin{align*}
x &amp;= \frac{dx}{dy}dy \\
&amp;= \tan \alpha \:d (C \sin^2 \alpha) \\
&amp;=2C \sin^2 \alpha \: d \alpha \\
&amp;= C(\alpha -\frac{1}{2} \sin 2 \alpha )
\end{align*}
$$

综上

$$
\begin{cases}
x &amp;= C(\alpha -\frac{1}{2} \sin 2 \alpha ) \\
y &amp;= C (1 -\frac{1}{2} \cos 2 \alpha )
\end{cases}
$$"><p>由能量守恒</p><p><mjx-container class="MathJax" jax="SVG" display="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="26.65ex" height="4.588ex" role="img" focusable="false" viewBox="0 -1342 div.data-content:
由能量守恒

$$mgy = \frac{1}{2} m v^2 \Rightarrow v = \sqrt{2gy}$$

即

$$v \cdot \frac {1} {\sqrt {y}} = \sqrt {2g} = \text{Const}$$

不失一般性, 考虑

$$v \cdot f(x, y) = \text{C}$$

曲线设为$x(t), y(t)$

则

$$ds = \sqrt {(dx)^2 + (dy)^2} = \sqrt {\dot x^2 + \dot y^2} dt$$

$$dt = \frac{ds}{v} = \text{C} f(x, y) ds = \text{C} f \sqrt {\dot x^2 + \dot y^2} dt$$

要求用时$T$最小

$$T = \int dt = C \int f \sqrt {\dot x^2 + \dot y^2} dt$$

根据哈密顿原理有:

$$\frac{\partial L}{\partial \boldsymbol {q}}-\frac{d}{dt}\frac{\partial L}{\partial \dot{\boldsymbol {q}}}=0$$

where

$$L = f \sqrt {\dot x^2 + \dot y^2}$$

由于本题

$$
\begin{align*}
f &= f(y) \\
\Rightarrow \frac{\partial f}{\partial x} &= 0 \\
\Rightarrow \frac{\partial L}{\partial x} &= 0
\end{align*}
$$

故只需考虑$x$方向

$$\frac{d}{dt}\frac{\partial L}{\partial \dot{x}}=0$$

故

$$\frac{\partial L}{\partial \dot{x}}=C$$

即

$$\frac{\dot x}{\sqrt {\dot x^2 + \dot y^2}} f = C$$

$$
\begin{align*}
&\quad \frac{\dot x}{\sqrt {\dot x^2 + \dot y^2}} f = C \\
&\Rightarrow \frac{1}{\sqrt {1 + (y^{\prime})^2}} f = C \\
&\Rightarrow \frac{1}{\sqrt {1 + (y^{\prime})^2}} \frac {1} {\sqrt {y}} = C \\
&\Rightarrow y(1 + (y^{\prime})^2) = C \\
\end{align*}
$$

注意到

$$\sin^2 \alpha (1+ \cot^2 \alpha) = 1$$

令

$$
\begin{cases}
y &= C \sin^2 \alpha \\
y^{\prime} &= \cot \alpha
\end{cases}
$$

则

$$
\begin{align*}
x &= \frac{dx}{dy}dy \\
&= \tan \alpha \:d (C \sin^2 \alpha) \\
&=2C \sin^2 \alpha \: d \alpha \\
&= C(\alpha -\frac{1}{2} \sin 2 \alpha )
\end{align*}
$$

综上

$$
\begin{cases}
x &= C(\alpha -\frac{1}{2} \sin 2 \alpha ) \\
y &= C (1 -\frac{1}{2} \cos 2 \alpha )
\end{cases}
$$
